# Swordjin Godot Development Progress

## Current Build Info
- Engine: Godot 4.4.1-stable (GL Compatibility)
- Target: Mobile PWA via HTML5 export
- Resolution: 640×360 (scales to mobile)

## Session: 2026-05-12

### Completed This Session
- [x] Godot project initialized with .gitignore
- [x] Mobile touch controls (virtual joystick + ATK/SKILL buttons)
  - Auto-detects mobile vs desktop
  - Desktop hides controls, mobile shows overlays
- [x] Chapter data system (JSON + MD pipeline)
  - ChapterDatabase autoload loads from res://chapters/actNN/
  - chapter001.md + chapter001.json for Act 1, Ch 1
- [x] GameState autoload (save/load, XP, level, unlocks)
  - Persistent JSON save in user://swordjin_save.json
  - Level up system with quadratic XP curve
  - Chapter completion tracking
- [x] LevelManager script (loads chapter data, spawns enemies, tracks objectives)
- [x] Main scene updated for dynamic chapter loading

### Architecture
Swordjin_Godot/
├── project.godot              # Autoloads: GameState, ChapterDatabase
├── scenes/
│   ├── main.tscn             # LevelManager + player + walls
│   ├── player.tscn           # CharacterBody2D, attack hitbox
│   ├── skeleton.tscn         # Enemy AI with detection + attack
│   └── mobile_controls.tscn  # Touch joystick + buttons
├── scripts/
│   ├── autoload/
│   │   ├── game_state.gd     # Save/load, progression
│   │   └── chapter_database.gd # JSON chapter loader
│   ├── player.gd             # Input, combat, HP
│   ├── skeleton.gd           # Chase AI, attack, death
│   ├── level_manager.gd      # Chapter setup + objective tracking
│   └── mobile_controls.gd    # Touch input mapping
└── chapters/
    └── act01/
        ├── chapter001.json   # Data (enemies, dialogue, rewards)
        └── chapter001.md     # Design doc

